nt-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black;\">Классификация по эксплуатационным свойствам</span></span><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: #555555; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; font-weight: normal;\">.</span></span></h3>\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"margin-left: -9.4pt; background: #F8F9FA; border-collapse: collapse; border: none; mso-border-alt: solid #A2A9B1 .75pt; mso-yfti-tbllook: 1184;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"border: solid #A2A9B1 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: solid #A2A9B1 .75pt; background: #EAECF0; padding: 2.4pt 4.8pt 2.4pt 4.8pt;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; margin: 12.0pt 0cm 12.0pt 0cm;\" align=\"center\"><b><span lang=\"RU\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black;\">Группа масел по</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 6.0pt 0cm 6.0pt 0cm;\" align=\"center\"><b><span lang=\"RU\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black;\">эксплуатационным свойствам</span></b></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"border: solid #A2A9B1 1.0pt; border-left: none; mso-border-left-alt: solid #A2A9B1 .75pt; mso-border-alt: solid #A2A9B1 .75pt; background: #EAECF0; padding: 2.4pt 4.8pt 2.4pt 4.8pt;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><b><span lang=\"RU\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black;\">Состав масел</span></b></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"border: solid #A2A9B1 1.0pt; border-left: none; mso-border-left-alt: solid #A2A9B1 .75pt; mso-border-alt: solid #A2A9B1 .75pt; background: #EAECF0; padding: 2.4pt 4.8pt 2.4pt 4.8pt;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><b><span lang=\"RU\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-s