fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-ansi-language: RU;\">- \"более дизельное\". Наличие букв ЕС после обозначения масла по </span><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black;\">API</span><span lang=\"RU\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-ansi-language: RU;\"> означает </span><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black;\">Energy</span> <span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black;\">Conserving</span><span lang=\"RU\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-ansi-language: RU;\">, т. е. энергосберегающее. Римская цифра </span><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black;\">I</span><span lang=\"RU\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-ansi-language: RU;\"> говорит об экономии топлива не менее 1,5%; </span><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black;\">II</span><span lang=\"RU\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-ansi-language: RU;\"> - не менее 2,5; </span><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black;\">III</span><span lang=\"RU\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-ansi-language: RU;\">