        '<div style=\"border-top: none; border-right: none; border-left: none; border-image: initial; border-bottom: 1pt solid #a2a9b1; padding: 0cm; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Motor oils – is important element</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">  </span>  </span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify;\">used for lubrication of engine. Undergoing thermal, mechanical</span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify;\">  </span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify;\">and chemical effects in lubrication system and on surfaces of lubricated and cooled parts of engine,</span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify;\">   </span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify;\">it provides long-term and reliable protection from wear of its moving parts.</span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify;\">  </span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify;\">Compatibility of engine design, performance conditions and</span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify;\">  </span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify;\">oil properties – are main principles for attaining high reliability</span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify;\">  </span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify;\">in</span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify;\">  </span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify;\">performance engine.</span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify;\">  </span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify;\">Modern motor oils shall meet the series of standards, including /but not limited to:</span> </td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table style=\"width: 1200px;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 600px;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\"> </span><span style=\"text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol; color: black;\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">        </span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\">High cleaning, dispersion-stabilizing and  solubilizating properties against insoluble dirt, providing cleanness of working parts of engine.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\